description.en:
$BEER is the new ERC20-token that gives 12-22% redistribution in the world’s hottest cryptocurrency: Ethereum.

$BEER doesn’t just give Ethereum rewards: it’s aimed at building a community and ultimately, it’s own beer brand, pubs – a beer empire. Paying with $BEER is the ultimate mission.

When you buy $BEER, relax and hodl for Ethereum. Buy more to see it create it’s own commercial empire.
